Ground the enriched Russian tomato surfaces in real Wikidata lexeme data
(issue #538). L3526 carries singular помидор / plural помидоры forms and a
sense grounded in Q23501; L170542 carries singular томат / plural томаты.
Both .json (raw, pretty-printed) and .lino (canonical lossless encoding)
snapshots pass wikidata_lino_cache_rebuilds_full_json_losslessly.
