MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Add a second agentic recipe (src/agentic_coding/meaning_detail.rs) so the
in-repo agentic loop — Formal AI driven through its OpenAI-compatible server —
edits its own seed knowledge. The recipe walks search -> fetch (Wikidata tomato
lexemes) -> write -> verify -> final and re-derives the enriched tomato block
byte-for-byte from the fetched lexeme facts: every surface pinned to part of
speech and grammatical number, grounded in its Wikidata form, with the
previously missing Russian plural томаты (L170542-F7) recovered.

- planner: dispatch #538 meaning-detail tasks to a dedicated recipe step
- corpus: add the tomato Wikidata lexeme page for offline search/fetch
- tests: byte-for-byte pin against data/seed/meanings-translation.lino plus a
  full end-to-end driver run (tests/unit/issue_538_agentic.rs)
