From: konard <drakonard@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 1 Jul 2026 15:56:45 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 13/44] refactor(agentic): make the meaning-detail recipe a
 concept registry (#538)

Generalize the issue-#538 recipe from tomato-specific to a Concept
registry so the *same* deterministic loop can make any registered
meaning more detailed, routed from the request via concept_for_task.
Tomato behavior is byte-for-byte unchanged; corpus now serves one
Wikidata-lexeme page per concept automatically.

Also fix a real TOCTOU race in AgentWorkspace::for_prompt: two agent
runs with the same prompt derived the same directory and raced on
remove_dir_all/create_dir_all. Each workspace now gets a unique
pid+sequence suffix (the path is never asserted on, only its contents),
so concurrent same-task runs no longer collide.
