timeouts, so it went red after adding the Agent CLI E2E job. Add the
job to the expected list at position 12 (right after test-e2e-local,
before deploy-demo) with a 20-minute timeout — deliberately larger
than test-e2e-local's 15 because this job cold-builds
`target/release/formal-ai` on the CI cache miss.
