+      # Each recipe axis of issue #538 is driven live through the real Agent CLI
+      # against the real formal-ai server — no in-repo simulation. Every step
+      # boots the server, drives the CLI with a *differently worded* request, and
+      # asserts the CLI exits 0, wrote the expected file, the file carries the
+      # requirement's canary string, and the loop walked ≥MIN_POSTS chat rounds.
