- self_ast recipe parses a real module of the meta algorithm (planner.rs)
  through the meta-language links network and records the abstract-syntax
  node census in Links Notation — general over any Rust source.
- route it first in plan_chat_step (most-specific router) so a task that
  names its output format 'Links Notation' is not stolen by the formalize
  keyword match.
- commit the generated data/meta/self-ast.lino and the Agent-CLI session,
  both reproduced byte-for-byte by the in-repo driver.
- move self_ast unit tests out of src/ (source-placement rule) into the
  issue-538 integration suite; add router-precedence + parity pins.
- add a 4th live Agent-CLI E2E step (port 8771) and reproduce-script axis.
